Subject: [PATCH] mm/mmap.c: Add cond_resched() for exit_mmap() CPU stalls
References: bnc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.8.2
Git-commit: 0a3b3c253a1eb2c7fe7f34086d46660c909abeb3

[ Upstream commit 0a3b3c253a1eb2c7fe7f34086d46660c909abeb3 ]

